'''Shiica''' ([[ingiriis]]: Shia; [[carabi]]: شيعة‎ "Shīʿah") waa waaxda labaad ee ugu weyn diinta [[Islaam]]ka. Ereyga Shiica waxa laga keenay Shīʻatu Calī (شيعة علي) micnaheedu yahay "raacayaashii" ama "taageerayaashii" asxaabigii [[Cali bin Abi Dalib]], ee [[nabi]] [[Muxamed]] (N.N.K.H) ilma-adeerka ahaayeen.

